         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><seg type="letterhead"><seg rend="left"><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00827-000-00001"/><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="small-caps">Dr.</hi><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><hi rend="capitals"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb294754">Wilhelm
                           Ginsberg</rs></hi></hi></seg><seg rend="right"><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb140"><hi rend="capitals">Halle</hi><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><hi rend="small-caps">a.</hi><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><hi rend="capitals">S.</hi></rs><hi rend="small-caps">, d.</hi></hi><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><date>10. Mai 1912</date></seg></seg><seg rend="right" type="letterhead"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="capitals"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb300422">Lafontainestr. 36</rs>.</hi></hi></seg><salute>Sehr geehrter Herr Doctor!</salute></opener><p>Die herzlichsten Wünsche zum <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L04016-1"/>Geburtstage<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L04016-1">Am <ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" target="1912-05-15" subtype="date-only"/> beging
            <rs type="person" ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler</rs> seinen 50. Geburtstag.</note> und verbindlichste Grüße in alter,
               unwandelbarer Verehrung</p><closer><signed>Elsa Ginsberg-Plessner.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
